            <title>[MAHOUT-324] conf.setMapOutputValueClass(vectorClass) should be conf.setMapOutputValueClass(Text.class); in KMeansDrive.runClustering(...)</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MAHOUT-324</link>
                <project id="12310751" key="MAHOUT">Mahout</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It looks to me the MapOutputValueClass is not set correctly in the method KMeansDrive.runClustering(...). , which doesn&apos;t match the OutputCollector used by the KMeansClusterMapper. Although it doesn&apos;t affect the output in the current implementation since the mapred.reduce.tasks is set to 0, it should be corrected.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Please confirm if this bug is valid.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
